--- !u!114 &1186121512
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1186121507}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: f944806bc10d40148af2908fb6c2749e, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  speakerName: Rabbit
  dialogueLines:
  - Oh, you found me.
  - 'Do not stare at me like that.


    I am only a rabbit.'
  - Well... maybe not only a rabbit.
  - 'He drew me here before he left.

'
  - 'He said you might need something to make the jump.


    Press "Enter" to dash.'
  - 'Dash can help you cross wider gaps.


    You only have one dash before touching
    the ground again.'
  - 'He is not here.


    He is waiting at the summit.'
  - 'But he can still see you.


    So keep going.'
  - He has been waiting for a very long time.
  triggerOnlyOnce: 1
