  speakerName: Unknown
  dialogueLines:
  - 'Awake, finally. '
  - 'It is normal to forget things after such a change.

    Do not be afraid of
    this body.'
  - 'Keep moving forward through the dark snow.

    At the end of this mountain,
    you will find the truth you desired.'
  - Your body still remembers how to move.
  - 'Move with "W A S D"


    Use "space" to jump, hold it to jump further, and
    be careful of the spikes.'
  - Try to live... and good luck
  triggerOnlyOnce: 1
